---
import SectionHead from './SectionHead.astro';
---
<section class="local">
  <div class="local__inner">
    <SectionHead eyebrow="Know your suburb" title="Plumbing in Happy Valley" />
    <div class="local__cols">
      <p class="reveal">
        Happy Valley has a mix of established homes, and many were built before modern plumbing
        standards. We often find old cast-iron and earthenware pipes under these properties. Over
        the years they rust, crack and let tree roots in. If your home is one of the older ones near
        the reservoir, a camera inspection is the fastest way to see what is really going on before
        a small problem becomes a big one.
      </p>
      <p class="reveal">
        The leafy streets that make Happy Valley such a nice place to live also cause plenty of root
        intrusion. Mature gum trees and established gardens send roots straight into joints and old
        clay drains. We see it across the suburb every week. Because we work in Happy Valley all the
        time, we know the local soil, the common pipe layouts and the quirks of homes here. That
        local knowledge means we find the cause faster, and we fix it properly the first time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .local { padding: clamp(64px,8vw,104px) 0; }
  .local__inner { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 clamp(16px,4vw,40px); }
  .local__cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: clamp(28px,4vw,56px); }
  .local__cols p { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #41515f; margin: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .local__cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 22px; } }
</style>
